                "Mandatory proactive LSP context (prefetched before first reply). Prioritize these real LSP diagnostics/errors over speculation. Do not call the lsp tool just to rediscover the same issues unless you need deeper navigation details.\n\n{}",
                sections.join("\n\n---\n\n")
            ),
        }],
    })
}
"}

